  <title><xmlelement>toc</xmlelement></title>
  <shortdesc>The <xmlelement>toc</xmlelement> element either references a
    topic that contains a table of contents for the book, or it indicates
    to a processor that a table of contents should be generated at this
    location in the book.</shortdesc>
